{"tid":2353160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打甩官司嘅手足，唔該真係唔好留係香港","createTime":"2021-01-04T13:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T07:08:01.000Z","uid":86295,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b13c31f7dd51938ece15386c1106114cdb0eb83","tid":2353160,"uid":86295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"我知好多手足好想留係香港，有就算俾政權打壓都會留喺香港嘅決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係，每單案件其實都係錢:<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"gold\"><strong>視乎案件視複雜程度，審訊可由幾日到幾星期，訟費可以由20萬到2百萬。</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/faqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Ffaqs&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=d5c5e0b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/faqs</a><br />\n<br />\n單Case一俾Dept of Joke上訴，唔好講入唔入，都已經等於燒咗612幾十萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能你話，叫多啲人課金咪得囉。但係，係現今政治氣候下，你又覺得係香港嘅612基金户口又可以捱幾耐？到時候，如果612俾人封左，又有邊個可以幫到你？<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果真係好撚鍾意香港嘅，就算唔怕打壓，為咗其他手足着想，希望可以好好考慮下離開香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1a283c5a61c0c78e380190a02ab5af7ae26f3a","tid":2353160,"uid":6845,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"申請左難民都無錢"},{"pid":"bbd576056c43cc5b4da06ecc404642b40cf86339","tid":2353160,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>申請做難民都無錢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f2a450af5242487597503c946a91671dc332ea11","tid":2353160,"uid":86295,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bbd576056c43cc5b4da06ecc404642b40cf86339","tid":2353160,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>申請做難民都無錢</blockquote>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"五眼都有救生艇計劃，有需要搵下幫手啦:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/H